Package: globalPM25
Title: Query Real-Time Local Air Pollute PM2.5 Level
Version: 0.1
Description: Query real-time local air pollute PM2.5 level near you, at any city around the world or within a user-defined geographical boundary. The real-time data soruce is coming from \url{aqicn.org}. First, Request your personal API token from \url{http://aqicn.org/data-platform/token/#/}. Set your personal token. Then you can query PM2.5 level near you, at any city or a list of cities worldwide, in any city area, or within a geographical boundary. 
Depends: R (>= 3.3.2)
Imports: jsonlite, tibble, dplyr, utils, ggplot2, stats, graphics
Suggests: testthat,
    knitr,
    rmarkdown
License: GPL(>=2)
Encoding: UTF-8
LazyData: true
